resources.string:
"Ukufaniswa kobuso kuvikeleke kancane kunephethini, iphinikhodi, noma iphasiwedi
Umuntu ofana nawe angakwazi ukuvula ithebulethi yakho
Idatha esetshenziselwa ukubona ubuso bakho igcinwa iyimfihlo kuthebulethi yakho"

"Thola indawo phakathi endlini engakhanyi kakhulu noma engekho mnyama kakhulu
Bamba ithebulethi kuleveli yeso"
Ukuze uvule ithebulethi yakho, vele uvule isikrini sakho uphinde ubheke ikhamera
Ithebulethi yakho izovula ngemuva nje kokuthi ikubone
